org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.batch.spi

Class OperationsQueue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.ogm.dialect.batch.spi.OperationsQueue

  • public class OperationsQueue
extends Object
    A queue for Operations.

    It keeps track of the elements that are going to be affected by an InsertOrUpdateTupleOperation. The queue can be closed, in that case it will throw an exception when trying to add or poll an operation.

    Author:
    Guillaume Scheibel <guillaume.scheibel@gmail.com>, Davide D'Alto <davide@hibernate.org>, Guillaume Smet
